  "slug": "natural-charcoal",
  "title": "Natural Charcoal",
  "description": "🔥🌳 Burned out logs have a chance to generate charcoal, which are immune to fire.",
  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://serilum.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/description/header/header.png\" alt=\"A Serilum Mod. Made with love. Lots of active mods for Fabric, Forge and Neo!\" width=\"838\" height=\"400\"></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://curseforge.com/members/serilum/projects\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://workflow.serilum.com/badges/svg/curseforge.svg&w=400\" alt=\"CurseForge\" width=\"200\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Serilum\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://workflow.serilum.com/badges/svg/modrinth.svg&w=400\" alt=\"Modrinth\" width=\"200\"></a> <a href=\"https://patreon.com/serilum\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://workflow.serilum.com/badges/svg/patreon.svg&w=400\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"200\"></a> <a href=\"https://youtube.com/@serilum\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://workflow.serilum.com/badges/svg/youtube.svg&w=400\" alt=\"YouTube\" width=\"200\"></a></p>\r\n<h2><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/about-the-mod.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"About the mod\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\"></h2>\r\n<p><span>Natural Charcoal makes wildfires useful! Whenever a log is destroyed via fire, it has a chance to drop charcoal. Charcoal is immune to fire, so it doesn't get destroyed by other fires nearby. By default it's a 2/3 chance for one to generate, though this can be changed in the config.<br><br>It is also possible to put logs next to a campfire to turn them into charcoal. This is slightly faster than using a furnace: Four pieces in 30 seconds instead of 40 when smelted.</span></p>\r\n<h2><br><br><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/dependencies.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"Dependencies\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\"></h2><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/collective\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/badges/dependencies/requires/collective.svg&w=502\" alt=\"Requires Collective\" width=\"251\" height=\"49\"></a><br><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/modpack/the-vanilla-experience\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/badges/dependencies/includes/the-vanilla-experience.svg&w=700\" alt=\"Included in The Vanilla Experience\" width=\"350\" height=\"49\"></a><br><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/badges/environment/server.svg&w=440\" alt=\"Environment: Server\" width=\"220\" height=\"49\"></p>\r\n<h2><br><br><br><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/configurable.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"Configurable\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\"></h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://serilum.com/configuration-guide\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/badges/configuration-guide.svg&w=440\" alt=\"Configuration guide\" width=\"220\" height=\"49\"></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;All available config options:</p>\r\n<details><summary>Show Spoiler</summary>\r\n<p><span><strong>charcoalIsImmuneToFire</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;default true<br>Whether the charcoal item should survive when being dropped inside fire.<br><br><span><strong>burnedLogBecomesCharcoalChance</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;default 0.67, min 0, max 1.0<br>The chance a log block that has been burned turns into charcoal.<br><br><span><strong>charcoalDropAmount</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;default 1, min 1, max 64<br>How much charcoal should be dropped from a burned log.</p>\r\n</details>\r\n<h2><br><br><br><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/showcase.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"Showcase\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\"></h2>\r\n<p><span><strong>A fire passed through the area! Useful, as it generates charcoal :)</strong></span><br><img src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/natural-charcoal/a.png\" alt=\"\"><br><br></p>\r\n<p><span><strong>Charcoal has a chance to drop whenever a log is destroyed via fire:</strong></span></p>\r\n<details><summary>Show Spoiler</summary>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/natural-charcoal/b.webp\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n</details>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><span><strong>It is also possible to create charcoal via the campfire:</strong></span></p>\r\n<details><summary>Show Spoiler</summary>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/natural-charcoal/c.webp\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n</details>\r\n<h2><br><br><br><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/notes-n-links.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"Notes and links\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\"></h2>\r\n<p><span><strong>You may freely use this mod in any modpack, as long as the download remains hosted within the CurseForge or Modrinth ecosystem.</strong></span><br><br><span><a href=\"https://serilum.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Serilum.com</a> contains an overview and more information on all mods available.</span><br><span><br>For issues, ideas, suggestions or anything else there is the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Serilum/.issue-tracker\" target=\"_blank\">Github repo</a>. Thanks!</span><span><br><br></span></p>",
